item.title: Follow the Lab Bunny on Twitter!
item.dc:creator: Sarah Cosper
item.description:
“One time beauty school suspendee, two time college dropout, full time lipstick hoarder. Libra. Non-smoker. DTF.” Follow me on Twitter for updates, quick tips, and probably hilarious jokes. At this price, how could you afford not to?
